---
title: Cheesy Mexican Bean Stuffed Capsicum with Leafy Rice & Sour Cream
description: Come on down to flavour town; tonight, it’s stuffed capsicums on the menu. Loaded with zesty beans, gooey cheese, and paired
with vibrant leafy rice, It’s a fiesta on your plate! Top it all off with a cooling dollop of sour cream and dig in.
